Invocation Name: pinoy quiz
des:
If you are from the Philippines, this app is for you ... You can find different questions from different topics in this skill.

Test your pinoyness with pinoy quiz!

Enjoy educational and fun trivia's with friends families and loved ones!

Available commands to start the game:
==============================================

* Alexa, start pinoy quiz
* Alexa, open pinoy quiz
* Alexa, play pinoy quiz


Available commands in game:
==============================================

* Answer 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 | 5
* To start a new game at any time, say, start game
* To repeat the last question, say, repeat
* Help
* Cancel
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
